I recommend to keep original docs. Some experts say a bit of useful articles are missing in new docs. Anyway this collection of docs is a must have for a .NET 1.x developer.
Original docs is October 2003 release. You can find it in torrent "Visual Studio .NET 2003 Enterprise - Full Discset". Some original Visual Studio .NET 2003 CDs contains older docs. These docs must be updated with the MS patch. To find it please look for "October 2003 Visual Studio .NET Documentation Update" on the MS web site.
